text: (beeping)

- [Announcer] AWS DeepRacer
is the fastest way

to get rolling on your
machine learning journey.
Developers of all skill levels,

including those with no prior
machine learning experience,
can take advantage of DeepRacer
by completing hands-on training
to build reinforcement models
to race for prizes and glory.
The DeepRacer ecosystem teaches you

the fundamentals of
reinforcement learning,
with educational resources,
an easy to use console,
and real self-driving RC cars.

Get started quickly with
interactive tutorials
and free workshops.
Walking step-by-step through the process,
DeepRacer helps you build your first
reinforcement learning model in minutes.

Go hands on with the
AWS DeepRacer console,
an environment to train and evaluate
your machine learning models.
This console environment helps build
the foundational skill sets to develop
reinforcement learning for any use case.
Once your model is created and trained,

the real fund begins in
the AWS DeepRacer League.
Developers compete monthly

by submitting their best
models to new tracks,
in an attempt to climb the leaderboard,
win prizes, and earn a qualifying spot

to race for the AWS
DeepRacer Championship Cup.

For even more fun with
reinforcement learning,
see your models at work in the real world,
with the AWS DeepRacer device,
a 1/18th scale fully autonomous car.
This allows you to observe and evaluate

your model's decision making
in a physical setting.

Shift your machine learning
journey into high gear,
and start racing today with AWS DeepRacer.
